        description: 'Peru once again ranks first in Latin America and the Caribbean in the implementation of trade facilitation measures, according to the latest update of the UN Global Survey on Digital and Sustainable Trade Facilitation 2025 (see here). The country increased its overall implementation score from 84.95% to 87.1% compared to 2023.',
